## Context
The paper classifies works into four quadrants by language x geography. This
requires author affiliation data from OpenAlex, estimated at 70-80% coverage.
Works without affiliations cannot be classified, weakening the analysis.

If fewer than 60% of works are classifiable, the quadrant analysis is unreliable
and the paper must be rescoped or abandoned.

## Actions
1. Read multilingual_report.json: quadrant_stats.unclassified
2. Compute classifiable fraction = 1 - unclassified / total
3. Decide: >=60% proceed, <60% investigate whether coverage can be improved

## Exit criteria
Go/no-go decision recorded in ticket log with the coverage number.
